19:43.000 --> 19:46.663
<i>Competitive systems, such as
evolution and capitalism,</i>

19:46.727 --> 19:50.634
<i>are terriffic at creating
unpredictable change very quickly.</i>

19:50.981 --> 19:53.129
<i>It's the trial by error system.</i>

19:53.672 --> 19:56.611
<i>If you're looking for
a wide variety of output,</i>

19:56.694 --> 19:58.975
<i>competitive systems are the best.</i>

19:59.473 --> 20:04.395
<i>Not only will the product of such systems
