20:29.337 --> 20:31.192
<i>...and the skills are useful ones.</i>

20:31.753 --> 20:33.865
<i>In a system like  </i> Pong,<i>  however,</i>

20:34.097 --> 20:37.015
<i>you just wind-up
getteing better at playing</i> Pong.

20:37.527 --> 20:39.545
<i>A competitive system, also</i>

