24:46.032 --> 24:47.953
<i>that capitalism has enabled</i>

24:48.235 --> 24:50.069
<i>but also constrained.</i>

24:50.346 --> 24:51.645
<i>In the new world,</i>

24:51.727 --> 24:53.315
<i>we'll be able to relax</i>

24:53.416 --> 24:55.276
<i>and let technology do the job.</i>

24:55.903 --> 24:57.426
<i>Try it !</i>

24:58.169 --> 25:00.150
