to internalize control.

33:20.351 --> 33:24.554
<i>Smelling?   Playing?
"Mestur-bating?"</i>

33:24.694 --> 33:26.898
The moment a person
internalizes the control,

33:27.104 --> 33:31.349
{\an8}making it an integral part of their
psychological make-up and their thinking,

33:31.635 --> 33:33.139
{\an8}it becomes absolute.

33:33.507 --> 33:35.904
{\an8}There is no longer anything external
to that component.

33:35.947 --> 33:37.968
You don't have to be told
to behave anymore,

33:37.970 --> 33:39.051
you want to behave.

33:39.156 --> 33:41.130
Because you think it's
good for you.

33:41.281 --> 33:43.591
